{"tid":2199657,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"回頭是岸 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-09-12T11:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T11:21:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c10df5242fd545cc5a5625472988fc31b936758b","tid":2199657,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200912/CIWDL6YKFJCO3BQZTCXAJKDJX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200912%2FCIWDL6YKFJCO3BQZTCXAJKDJX4%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fzRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=02cdca01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200912%2FCIWDL6YKFJCO3BQZTCXAJKDJX4%2F&h=3877a809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200912/CIWDL6YKFJCO3BQZTCXAJKDJX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n回頭是岸 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VnaUfLdbRLYuJKAl8SiZcZsq4vA=/843x526/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FNMX5ZJOIZDBHBUK4QXMDIIV6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVnaUfLdbRLYuJKAl8SiZcZsq4vA%3D%2F843x526%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFNMX5ZJOIZDBHBUK4QXMDIIV6I.jpg&h=b7c8b745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《投奔怒海》劇照<br />\n<br />\n心中一直記掛投奔怒海的那十二人，關心着他們的消息，只希望上天垂憐，讓他們可以重新回航，不送中而送回港，就在自己的地方接受法律公平的以及合乎人道的審判。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼要鋌而走險，孤注一擲的投身驚濤駭浪中？。。。。。。。。。孰使由之孰令致之？<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n三十八年前年輕的許鞍華導演拍攝了那部「投奔怒海」，一部片捧紅了初出道後來成巨星的劉德華，而繆騫人、林子祥等演員也剛初試新聲，恐怕今天的許導演也想像不到三十多年後，就在香港海域竟發生了真實的投奔怒海這一幕，林鄭當特首時的香港發生了這一幕是不容抹去的恥辱！明知人微言輕，沒有人聽得進去也要呼籲：發生在香港的事就在香港解決吧。這有名有姓的十二位香港居民何需特地用巧妙設計把他們送中，政府應該向中國要回這十二位人質才是正道。"}]}